/-- Final contour-injection adapter for an oriented dual-edge traversal.
The remaining F4 geometry can now target exactly the data of a rooted
length-`≤ 2m` oriented walk that covers the candidate cut set. -/
theorem cutWalkCodeInjection_family_of_orientedCutWalk_exists
    (hwalk :
      ∀ m, 2 ≤ m → ∀ i ∈ Finset.range m, ∀ j ∈ Finset.range (m - (i + 1)),
