      (Mettapedia.Logic.MarkovLogicInfiniteCompactness.RegionExhaustion.isProjectiveMeasureFamily_of_tendsto_stageProbabilityFamily
        (E := gridExhaustion) (M := M) (ξ := gridMinusBoundary)
